snippet.title: Bagheera Kannada Official Trailer | Sriimurali & Rukmini | Dr Suri | Prashanth Neel | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
ROAR WITH EXCITEMENT!

Get ready for the ultimate action-packed ride! Watch the explosive trailer of #Bagheera, produced by Hombale Films, the makers of KGF, Kantara, and Salaar! 
Directed by Dr. Suri,  created by visionary director Prashanth Neel, Music by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and Produced by Vijay Kiragandur.

The countdown begins! Bagheera hits theaters on Oct 31st!

snippet.title: Jetha और Bhide ने जमकर लिए Popatlal के मज़े | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah |Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

In this exciting episode, Madhavi has reported a bike stolen from the market. Inspector Chalu Pande assures them that the search team is working to find the bike. Will the police be able to locate it? Watch the full episode to find out what happens.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1636
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTWbYoG3SaD_hKNC0g53ugi

snippet.title: #Video | Chocolatey Sadiya | चॉकलेटी सड़िया | Khesari Lal Yadav | Priyanka Singh | Rajaram | Sapna C
snippet.description:
तैयार हो जाईं  " चॉकलेटी सड़िया" के मस्तीभरा बीट्स पर झूमे खातिर ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और सपना चौहान के साथ चॉकलेटी अंदाज़ में

Subscribe to our channel for more
 Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Title - Chocolatey Sadiya
Hindi - चॉकलेटी सड़िया
Film : Rajaram राजाराम
Singer - Khesari Lal Yadav & Priyanka Singh
Music - Krishna Bedardi
Lyrics - Kundan Preet
Feat - Khesari Lal Yadav & Sapna Chauhan
Director: Parag Patil
Producer: Parag Patil, R.R. Prince
Choreographer: - Prasun Yadav

Film Credits:
Production: - Technician Film Factory 
Producers: - Parag Patil & R.R. Prince 
Director: - Parag Patil

Lyrics:-

मुखड़ा 
फीमेल : का देखत बड़ा ये राजा जी बोला 
बाड़ा छीपावाले का भेद दिल के खोला
फीमेल :  का देखत बड़ा ये राजा जी बोला 
बाड़ा छीपावाले का भेद दिल के खोला

मेल : एक त दूधिया गोराई, दूजा तिल करिया मे 
चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 

कोरस :चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 

अंतरा 
मेल : बिंदिया तोहार लागे आसमान के 
कोरस :- जाने ऐ गोरी 
मेल :- बसें हमार तोहरे नाथूनिया मे 
कोरस :- पारने ऐ गोरी 
फीमेल : एतना बखान करके जान लेबा का ऐ राजा 
निहिया के सजल कुल दुकान लेबा का ऐ राजा 
मेल : मन करें एकदम रखले रही अकवारिया मे 
चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 
कोरस :- चॉकलेटवे जइसन लागेलु चॉकलेटी सड़िया मे 

अंतरा २
मेल :- हीरा जइसन देह दूज कमशीन 
कोरस :- उमरिया ऐ गोरी 
मेल :-डाहे दूजे बज्जर तोर पतली 
कोरस :- कमरिया ऐ गोरी 
फीमेल :-एतना घूमवा जनी बतावा दिल के बतिया हो 
पोरे पोरे जानिले तोहार हम अदतिया हो 
मेल :- तोहार नियन ना फूल खिलाल कौनो फूलवारिया मे

snippet.title: Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum Episode 31 | Teaser | Fahad Mustafa | Hania Aamir | ARY Digital
snippet.description:
Watch all the episode of Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum here: https://bit.ly/3zNNsGu

Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum | Episode 31 | Teaser | Digitally Presented by Master Paints , foodpanda , Sunsilk & Skin White | Fahad Mustafa | Hania Aamir | 21 October 2024 | ARY Digital Drama 

The drama revolves around the concept of ‘Opposites Attract’ where Hania aka Sharjeena will portray the role of a bibliophile, topper and a sorted girl with a practical approach while Fahad’s character is a little laid-back.

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

nl.title: Racehoogtepunten | Grand Prix van de Verenigde Staten 2024
nl.description: Kom bij op het 12e bezoek van de Formule 1 aan het Circuit of the Americas, terwijl titelkandidaten Max Verstappen en Lando Norris tot aan de vlag streden in een intense strijd, terwijl Liam Lawson indruk maakte bij zijn terugkeer op de grid!

fr.title: Meilleurs moments | Grand Prix des Etats-Unis 2024
fr.description: Revivez la 12e visite de la F1 au circuit des Amériques, avec un combat jusqu'au drapeau à damier entre les rivaux pour le titre Max Verstappen et Lando Norris, ainsi qu'un retour convaincant de Liam Lawson en F1 !

pt.title: Melhores Momentos | Grande Prêmio dos Estados Unidos 2024
pt.description: Acompanhe a 12ª visita da Fórmula 1 ao Circuito das Américas enquanto os candidatos ao título Max Verstappen e Lando Norris lutavam até a bandeirada final em uma batalha intensa, enquanto Liam Lawson impressionava em seu retorno ao grid!

es.title: Mejores Momentos | Gran Premio de Estados Unidos 2024
es.description: Descubre lo que ha dado de sí la duodécima visita de la Fórmula 1 al Circuito de las Américas. Los rivales al título Max Verstappen y Lando Norris han peleado intensamente hasta que ha caído la bandera, además de un Liam Lawson que ha hecho un regreso impresionante a la parrilla.

CHOWK - 99side 

Dikhna mat chowk par bhokte
Khule bazaar mein kholte
Nahin sochta kya bolte chaar log hain
Bana dete chaar kandhon ka bojh hai
Hum lakadbagghe seedha nochte
Muft mein gang de rahi moksh hai
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Dikhna mat, dikhna mat
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Khule Bazaar mein kholte thokte
Kidhar se bolte Vile ke chhokre
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat
 Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte

Yerwada jail meri jaib kare Daandi ko qaid
Inhein sone ki na parakh tabhi chandi chunein
Tu chandi ka chammach mila bachpan se sab
Hum toofan kyunki janam diya aandhi ne hai
Hum bhakt hai Bhagat ke
khaulta rakht nass mein
Gulaami ke badle phaansi chunein
Mujhse jung matlab maafi kadaapi nahin
Lanka jalaa ke kardun tere naabi mein chhed
Banani mujhe Legacy jo hogi lambi Draupadi ke saree jaise
Likhta baareeki se bhaari paise chahiye shabdon ke
kyunki shabdon ka kaarigar main
Paison ke paudhon ko ugaate
hum mehnat paseene se
Hustle ye maali jaise
Jo bole paise se milti khushi nahin
Bol raha woh munh se nahi pichhwaade se hai
Dogle log ke thopde fode
Tu phuski bam hum Tope ke gole
Tu weak hai bahut hum potte Boss hai
Hum se lafde matlab khoon se lathpath,
Jaise bacche aate kokh se.
Bahaayega khoon galey milayegi maut
Bahaayega paseena kamaayega note
Kamaayega note to gawaayega apne

Waqt ke na saath par waqt badal doon
Tune chheena mera haqq tera takth badal doon 
Gaane likhe Maine saare sab qatal doon
Tu ne kare kaafi jhol khud se kar kuch
Zyaada bak mat chote mere haat ka mal tu
Bandana pehne par thug nahin hai tu
Dikhta na zyada main jaise full moon
Chhote cheel ki chonch hoon saanp leke udd loon
Dekhe tere jaise bane shaane
Peeth peeche bakey baatein
Mere baare tere baare mein
na thoda bhi sochun
Main karun joh bhi mann bole na ki baaki jann bole
Bhediyon ke bheed mein tu bakri ghonchu
Lage mere saare peeche, gulaabi note hoon
Girne waale ko utha doon aisi chot hoon
Vigyaan bhi na pahonche vigyaan bhi na soche main aisi khoj hoon

Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Dikhna mat, dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Khule Bazaar mein kholte
Nahin sochta kya bolte chaar log hai 
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Dikhna mat , dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Khule Bazaar mein kholte thokte Kidhar se bolte Vile ke chokre
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Vile Parle, Bambai sheher, 99side, Dikhna mat chowk pe Lala

Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Khule bazar mein kholte
Nahin sochta kya bolte chaar (4) log hai
Banaa dete chaar (4) kandhon ka bojh hai
Hum lakadbagghe seedha nochte
Muft mein gang de rahi moksh hai
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte Dikhna mat , dikhna mat 

Jali jali teri mere se jali toh phir jadibooti lagaake tu thandi kara le
Khade khade tujhe bata doon mere kalam mein kitni taakat jo ki teri garmi utaare
Fati padi teri tabhi jabhi likhi maine tere barein mein ye sabi sacchi jo baatein
Nahin bhoolunga woh raatein
Jo bhi bina khaana khaate
Bina sote likhe maine gaane
Jo bhi tere saath hai
sacche waade nahin nibhaate
Badi baatein par bahaane
Maine likhe sacche gaane
Hum karke dikhaate tum karte dikhaave
Mere baaton mein jo baat
Tere baaton mein na baat hai
Main baatein badhaa doon tere paas baatein karne ko na baat hai
Jo bhi saath mere khaas hai
Aata jahan se milte bas jhaanse
Tu nahin khaas hai
banta bas khaas hai
nikal na yahan se
Rehta main khud hi mein magan
Duniyadari se nahin hai lain dain
Funny dekh kitni yahan game hai
Saare rappers sound hote hain same same
Jo naak ghista khud
wahi dusron ko bolta hai shembde
Alien rapperon ke liye bhai tera Ben-10

snippet.description:
In the #MSCKBFC showdown, Mohammedan SC started strong, taking an early lead courtesy of a penalty in the first half of the game. However, #KeralaBlastersFC came out firing in the second half to  flip the game on its head. #KBFC  netted two crucial goals in quick succession that turned the tide in their favour. Despite #MSC's early advantage, #KBFC’s second-half comeback saw them seal a 2-1 victory.

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Mayara Ma Joyi Manadu Munjay Che | New Gujarati Bewafa Song 2024
snippet.description:
Feeling the pain of lost love? Listen to Rakesh Barot's new heartbreak song, "Mayara Ma Joyi Manadu Munjay Che" only on @SaregamaGujarati  🎶

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Neha Suthar
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Lyrics: Chirag Barot 
Music: Mayur Nadiya 
Co.artist: Sharmaji, Lata Prajapati, Soham Chhatral Wala Group, Dharati Patel, Krish Jaani
Dop: Arvind Motap 
Video Editing: Kishor Rajput 
Make Up: Chirag Parmar
Hairdresser: Mandakini 
Assistant Director: Babusinh Thakor
Production Management: Jigar Panchal
Spot Boy: Kiran Thakor, Viru Thakor, Pravin Vadu
Food Management: Village Vila Cafe 
Poster Design: Aman Agola 
Sp.thanks: Manish Patel, Divyang Patel

Lyrics:

તને માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
ઓ યારા...ઓ યારા....
ઓ યારા...ઓ યારા....
તને માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે...(2)
 
તું નથી બેવફા કેમ બેવફા થાય છે
નથી બેવફા કેમ બેવફા થાય છે
તને માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
હો તને માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
 
હો કરવી હતી મારે પ્રેમ ભરી વાતો
તારો ને મારો હતો રુદિયા નો નાતો....(2)
મને નોતી ખબર તું મારાથી દૂર જાય છે
નોતી ખબર તું મારાથી દૂર જાય છે
તને માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
હો માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
 
હો ખોટો તારો પ્રેમ ને ખોટી તારી વાતો
તું તો સમજાવી ગઈ રીત ને રિવાજો...(2)
જે હતો વિશ્વાસ આજે તૂટી જાય છે
હતો વિશ્વાસ આજે તૂટી જાય છે
તને માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
ઓ માયરામાં જોઈ મારું મનડું મૂંઝાય છે
 
 
Tane Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che
O Yaara….o Yaara…
O Yaara….o Yaara…
Tane Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che…(2)
 
Tu Nathi Bewafa Kem Bewafa Thay Che
Nathi Bewafa Kem Bewafa Thay Che
Tane Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che
Ho Tane Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che
 
Ho Karavi Hati Mare Prem Bhari Vaato
Taro Ne Maro Hato Rudiya No Naato…(2)
Mane Noti Khabar Tu Marathi Door Jaay Che
Noti Khabar Tu Marathi Door Jaay Che
Tane Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che
Ho Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che
 
Ho Khoto Taro Prem Ne Khoti Tari Vaato
Tu To Samjavi Gai Rito Ne Rivajo…(2)
Je Hato Vishwas Aaje Tuti Jaay Che
Hato Vishwas Aaje Tuti Jaay Che
Tane Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che
Oo Mayarama Joyi Maru Manadu Munjay Che

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: करवा चौथ 2024 - ॐ जय करवा मैया - Karwa Chauth Aarti - Om Jai Karwa Maiya - करवा माता की आरती
snippet.description:
Karva Chauth or Karwa Chauth or Karaka Chaturthi is aHindu festival celebrated by Hindu women of Northern and Western India in October or November on the Hindu lunar month of Kartika. 

करवा चौथ हिन्दुओं का एक प्रमुख त्योहार है। यह भारत के जम्मू, हिमाचल प्रदेश, पंजाब, उत्तर प्रदेश, हरियाणा, मध्य प्रदेश और राजस्थान में मनाया जाने वाला पर्व है। यह कार्तिक मास की कृष्ण पक्ष की चतुर्थी को मनाया जाता है। यह पर्व सौभाग्यवती स्त्रियाँ मनाती हैं।

► Album - Karwa Mata Ki Aarti
► Song - Karwa Mata Ji Ki Aarti
► Singer - Rinky Vishwakarma
► Music - Satish Dehra 
► Lyrics - Traditional
➤ Label - Vianet Media
➤ Sub Label - Ambey
➤ Parent Label - Shubham Audio Video Pvt. Ltd.

Jaan Nisar Episode 64 Teaser - 19th October 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan
Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Bhide informs everyone that the order has been cancelled, everyone tries to help him sell all the boxes of chocolates but fail to sell even a single box, just then Sonu comes home and informs everyone that someone has offered to buy all the boxes and he is coming to the society in the evening. Who is this secret angel?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

Click here to watch episodes from TMKOC: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn5vww_8o5KtB8mEbckPmk4F9mKzG1qUm

Family Dairies follows the everyday life of a middle-class family—a father, mother, and their only son—as they navigate the ups and downs of modern family life. The father works hard to provide, while the mother nurtures the family’s emotional core. Their son faces the pressures of growing up, balancing family expectations with his own dreams. Each episode highlights the family's interactions with friends and relatives, portraying the challenges, joys, and lessons that come with maintaining love and harmony in their lives.

A Dreamz Unlimited Production.

At Babita's house, Gokuldham Society members supervise the washing machine while planning a pizza party. As the cast and crew embark on a religious pilgrimage to commemorate the show's nine-year triumph, Bhide reflects on some of the most memorable moments.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi
Episode - 2257

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy #tmkoc #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch the 'Comedy Lagataar' episodes from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZAg6W-3De1ssi64wfuZyw6

snippet.title: OH HELLO! - A COMEDY SPECIAL BY RAHUL DUA | 2024
snippet.description:
The Greatest Comedy Special of all time, that's it. That's the description, thank you for reading.

Oh. And don’t miss the surprise at the end. Before the credits’ roll. You wouldn’t have seen anything like this before. 

My First Ever Standup Comedy Special - 4 years of writing, rehearsing, crafting and perfecting jokes. It’s super tight, it’s relatable, it’s hilarious. And now, it’s all yours!

I won’t ask you to leave a LIKE, SHARE the video, COMMENT for better reach & to buy my live shows’ tickets - because the special is so good you’ll do it automatically. 

Thanks for reading. Much love to all of you.
Tickets to my live shows (domestic and international): https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour

snippet.title: EXCLUSIVE: MOHD SHAMI ON HIS IPL RETENTION WITH GUJARAT TITANS AND COMEBACK PLANS FOR AUSTRALIA TOUR
snippet.description:
In an exclusive interview with Sports Tak fast bowler Mohammed Shami has proclaimed that he is fully fit and is aiming a comeback in the Border Gavaskar Trophy against Australia. Shami, who has not played a competitive game since ODI World Cup 2023, said that he wants to play a couple of Ranji Trophy games to get match-fit.

The pacer has been at the National Cricket Academy since his ankle surgery after the World Cup, and has been rehabilitating under the watchful eyes of the Board of Control for Cricket in India medical staff. Shami was recently seen bowling with a strapped knee at the centre wicket after the Bengaluru Test match.

Aafat Episode 05 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Abbas - Hibba Aziz - 21st October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Warisha is a beautiful yet short-tempered girl living with her mother and stepfather. Warisha has
followed the same misguided path that her mother, Mehak, took in the past. Influenced by her
parents, Warisha has developed a greedy nature.

Wahaj, Warisha's paternal cousin, is a handsome young man in love with his cousin Shifa.
However, neither Wahaj nor Shifa knows that Warisha is jealous of Wahaj and has bad
intentions towards him and his family.

Will Warisha’s jealousy harm Wahaj’s love? Can Shifa and Wahaj marry with Warisha standing
in their way? Will Warisha make a bad choice due to her parents’ influence? Will Wahaj and
Shifa uncover Warisha’s real intentions?

सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.
ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी | To Order -
 • Website - https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/
 • Amazon - https://www.amazon.in/s?me=A6FSX0SQK7GV6&marketplaceID=A21TJRUUN4KGV

1Kg Chakli Bhajani Recipe
१ किलो चकली भाजणी प्रमाण | फूड बीजनेस | दिवाळी फराळ ऑर्डर | ऑर्डर साठी चकली भाजणी | चकलीची भाजणी किंवा भाजणीची चकली रेसिपी | खमंग चकली भाजणी रेसिपी व खुसखुशीत चकली | कमी तेलकट चकलीची खास टिप्स | परफेक्ट चकली भाजणी रेसिपी | चकली भाजणी रेसिपी | चकलीची भाजणी | सरिता किचन चकली भाजणी |

साहित्य | Ingredients
चकली भाजणीसाठी | For Chakali Bhajani Flour
वजनी प्रमाण (१ किलो भाजणी साठी ) | Gram Measurements ( for 1 kg chakali bhajani)
 • तांदूळ अर्धा किलो | Rice ½ kilo
 • हरभरा डाळ २०० ग्राम | Bengal Gram dal 200 Gram
 • पिवळी मूग डाळ १०० ग्राम | Yellow Moong Dal 100 Gram
 • उडीद डाळ ५० ग्राम | Urad Dal 50 gram
 • पोहे १०० ग्राम | Poha 100 Gram
 • साबुदाणा १०० ग्राम | Sago 100 Gram
 • धने २० ग्राम | Coriander Seeds 20 Gram
 • जिरे १० ग्राम | Cumin Seeds 10 Gram
 कप चे प्रमाण / वाटीचे प्रमाण | Cup Measurements
 • तांदूळ ४ कप | Rice 4 cups
 • हरभरा डाळ दीड कप | Chana daal 1.5 Cup
 • पिवळी मूग डाळ पाऊण कप | Yellow Moong Dal ¾ Cup
 • उडीद डाळ अर्धा कप | Urad Daal ½ Cup
 • पोहे १ कप | Poha 1 Cup
 • साबुदाणा पाऊण कप | Sago ¾ Cup
 • धने पाव कप | Coriander Seeds ¼ Cup
 • जिरे २ टेबलस्पून | Cumin Seeds 2 tbsp

चकलीसाठी | For Making Chakali Recipe
वजनी प्रमाण | Gram Measurements
 • तयार चकली भाजणी १ किलो | Ready Chakali Bhajani Flour 1 kg
 • तेल ९० - १०० ग्राम | Oil 90-100 Gram
 • ओवा १ टीस्पून | Carom Seeds 1tsp
 • पांढरे तीळ १/४ कप | Sesame 1/4cup
 • मिरची पावडर ४ टीस्पून | Chilly pw 4 tsp
 • मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
 • कडकडीत गरम पाणी गरजेनुसार |Hot water as required 

८ कप / वाटीचे प्रमाण | 8 Cup Measurements
 • तयार चकली भाजणी ८ कप | Bhajani Flour 8 Cups
 • तेल १/२ कप | Oil ½ Cup 
 • ओवा १ टीस्पून | Carom Seeds ½ cup
 • तीळ १/४ कप | Sesame ¼ cup
 • मिरची पावडर ४ टीस्पून | Chilly pw 4 tsp
 • मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
 • गरम पाणी गरजेनुसार | Hot water as required

तयार चकली भाजणी ४ कप | Ready chakali bhajani flour 4 cups
 • तेल १/४ कप | Oil ¼ cup
 • ओवा १/२ टीस्पून | Carom seeds ½ tsp
 • तीळ २ टेबलस्पून | Sesame 2 tbsp
 • मिरची पावडर २ टीस्पून | Chilly pw 2 tsp
 • मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
 • गरम पाणी गरजेनुसार | Hot water as required

How to make Chakali Bhajani Recipe at home | how to make chakali bhajani 
 • Wash the rice, moong dal, urad dal, chana daal, separately
 • Keep them on to separate strainers for 10 mins to remove excess water
 • Then spread them onto separate cotton cloths under shadow for 2-3 hrs
 • Then heat up a heavy bottom kadhai, add rice & rosat it until rice changes the color to more whitish, get fluffy, once done take them onto a dry cotton cloth
 • Then into the same kadhai roast chana daal on low flame until they get light grill marks, once done, pour the roasted chana daal onto the roasted rice
 • Then dry roast moong dal followed by the urad daal & take them onto the cotton cloth
 • Then dry roast sabudana & poha separately on low flame & take them out
 • Lastly dry roast cumin seed & coriander seeds & take them out onto the roasted grains
 • Allow the roasted ingredients to cool down completely & them take them to a flour mill & grind fine powder
 • Our chakali bhajani is ready to make crispy chakali

How to make Kurkurit chakali recipe | how to make bhajanichi chakali recipe |
 • Take the bhajani flour into a large plate or parat.
 • to this add salt, sesame, carom seeds, chilly pw & mix everything well
 • Into a tadaka pan heat up oil, pour this piping hot onto the chakali bhajani flour, mix well & rub the oil all over the flour
 • Heat up some water, once water is about to boil turn off the flame, & knead the dough using hot water
 • carefully mix the flour using a spatula  into the hot water, cover it for 10 mins 
 • then using lukewarm water knead a tight dough
 • Our chakali dough is ready to make chakali.
 • take some dough from the ready dough, using some water knead the dough to make it soft (as shown in the video)
 • make a log out of it, put the log into the chakali mould, make the chakalis
 • heat up oil for frying the chakali, once oil is med hot, drop 3-4 chaklis, fry them on med flame
 • while frying keep the flame med, not too low or high

chakali recipe marathi https://youtu.be/V53g5kklhUo?si=DTJ-3QwYOeDHA-TP
 Shankarpali https://youtu.be/iesqDnyO1aM?si=kLrYbh6KWrLTr5qY

हलके जाळीदार अनारसे  https://youtu.be/qcplhSZ_trc?si=LYuMbU6FNb73Cfia
१ किलो भाजक्या पोह्यांचा चिवडा | Chiwada Recipe https://youtu.be/J4SVwldXoqA?si=t5Ijgi-NBj3yixU2

snippet.title: O Beliya Official Music Video | Darshan Raval | Ahsaas Channa | Naushad Khan | Out Of Control
snippet.description:
Step into a magical world of love with O Beliya, where every moment feels like a dream! Sung and composed by Darshan Raval, this mesmerizing track takes you on a journey of pure romance as two souls embrace the beauty of being together. Featuring the lovely Ahsaas Channa, this song captures the joy of love in its most wonderful form. With heartfelt lyrics by Gurpreet Saini and enchanting music produced by Lijo George, O Beliya is a celebration of love you’ll want to relive again and again!

snippet.title: Baapu | Ajitesh Bhati | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
This song is about me confessing to my father that I’m in love with a girl, and how it’s been a major distraction for me. I try to convince him by expressing my feelings for her, but he refuses to accept the relationship. In response, I decide to leave the house, capturing the emotional conflict and tension in our conversation.

Chhora tero bekaar ho gayo hai
Padhne likhne mein No mann lagto yaa ko 
Chhori ke chakkar mein 
Chhora barbaad ho gayo hai

 Hoo…

Ghar mein bhi dhundoon kona
Chhupne ku baapu te 
Ab kamre mein jo milgo
Kat jaungo chaaku te
Galti te kal takraago 
Baapu te aangan mein
Lathiye ki barsa kardi
Phir Baapu ne taangan mein
Baapu karvaato dikhe 
Byaah mero faagan mein
Baapu ne beej bo diya
Mere hi bhaagan mein

Hoo….

Meri gaadi mero paisa
Main kamaa ke laata hun
Meri gaadi mein
Saale londiya ghumaato tu ?
Ullu ke pattha 
mein ghoosa baja dunga
Reepat ke maare main 
Munh so sujaa dunga
Karaego mo su jo ondhi inn baatan ne
Saale Nikhattu hai ghar te bhaga dunga 

Ghar te nikalte hi Shawl baandh liyo
Half down tha Half aur daal liyo
Jhedd-pedd phir maine phon-phaan kiya 
Milaya baapu ko

O baapu mo pyaar ho gayo hai 
Chhora tero bekaar ho gayo hai
Ghar mein bhi yaako ab mann no lagto 
Chhori ke chakkar mein 
Ghar te faraar ho gyo hai

Hoo…
Baapu kar baitho pyaar main 
Chhori mein poore sanskar hain
Chhori ke ghar ke bhi taiyyar hain
Bas Baapu mein chho aar paar hai
O Baapu

Karwa Chauth Rangoli Ideas for 2024

Karwa Chauth, a festival celebrated by married women in India, involves rituals and traditions that often include creating beautiful Rangoli designs. Here are some ideas and tips for creating a stunning Rangoli for Karwa Chauth 2024:

Popular Rangoli Themes for Karwa Chauth
Traditional Motifs:

Use traditional designs such as peacocks, flowers, and geometrical patterns.
Incorporate symbols like the moon and stars to signify the festival's importance.
Colors of Festivity:

Utilize bright colors like red, orange, yellow, and gold to reflect the joyous spirit of the occasion.
Mix in white or green for contrast, using rice powder, colored powders, or flower petals.
Incorporating Elements of Worship:

Design Rangoli with elements like lamps (diyas), thalis (plates), and Karwa (the pot) to enhance the festive theme.
Create a circular design that can symbolize unity and completeness in relationships.
Personal Touches:

Include your name or initials within the Rangoli for a personal touch.
Use patterns that represent your family's traditions or values.
Tips for Making Rangoli
Choose the Right Location: Pick a prominent place near the entrance of your home or courtyard where it will be visible to guests.

Plan Your Design: Sketch your design on paper before executing it on the ground to avoid mistakes.

Use Natural Colors: If possible, use natural colors from flowers, turmeric, and other organic materials for an eco-friendly approach.

Add Accents: You can use small diyas or candles placed around the Rangoli for an enchanting effect in the evening.

शुभ मुहूर्त (Shubh Muhurat) for Karwa Chauth 2024
Karwa Chauth Date: October 20, 2024
Moonrise Timing: The moon will rise after sunset, so ensure you complete your fast and the rituals in time for the sighting of the moon.
Sample Rangoli Designs
Here are a few ideas for designs:

Floral Patterns: Create a floral border with a central design featuring the moon.
Circular Patterns: Design concentric circles with alternating colors to represent unity and love.
Themed Rangoli: Incorporate motifs of the husband and wife or symbolize prosperity and health.
Final Touch
Once you have created your Rangoli, be sure to maintain its beauty by keeping the area clean and avoiding foot traffic over it.

May your Karwa Chauth be filled with joy and prosperity, and may your Rangoli bring blessings to your home!

Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

snippet.title: PANDLOYAMMA PALLU || FULL SONG || FOLK SONG 2024 || INDRAJITT || PARSHURAM NAGAM ||
snippet.description:
WATCH : PANDLOYAMMA PALLU || PANDLOYAMMA PANDLU || FULL SONG || FOLK SONG 2024 || INDRAJITT |PARSHURAM NAGAM || KATHERAPAKA SRINIVAS


పాట నేపథ్యం:
*తెలంగాణ గ్రామీణ ప్రాంతాల్లో చాలా ప్రసిద్ధిగాంచిన కథని..  పాట రూపంలో తీసుకువస్తున్నాము.
*అక్రమాసంబంధ0 పెట్టుకున్న.. ఓ ఇల్లాలును తన కొడుకు నిలదీయడంతో.. ప్రబుద్ధుడు చంపేస్తాడు. శవాన్ని పూడ్చే క్రమంలో ఎన్నెన్నో ఇబ్బందులు ఎదురౌతాయి. 
*దాంతో.. ఇంట్లో.. కొడుకుని నిలువునా కోసి.. ఉప్పుకారం దట్టించి.. కూర వండుతుంది. అనుకోకుండా అప్పుడే.. భర్త రావడంతో... అదే కూరను.. భర్తకు వడ్డిస్తుంది. 
*భర్త తింటావుంటే.. కంచంలో కొడుకు యొక్క వెండి ఉంగరం..  బంగారి గొలుసు కనబడుతుంది.
*అంతే... మళ్ళీ ఆ ప్రబుద్ధుడు వచ్చి భర్తని కొట్టి సంపుతాడు. 
*కానీ అదంతా గమనిస్తున్న దొంగలు.. ఇంటికి గడియవేసి.. నిప్పు పెడతారు.  దాంతో ఈ రంకు జంట కూడా బూడిద అయిపోతుంది. 

నీతి:  తాత్కాలిక ఆనందాల కోసం.. పాకులాడితే.. నా అనుకునే వాళ్లనే కాదు.. చివరికి తనకు తాను సర్వం కోల్పోతారు అని.. చాటి చెప్పే పాట ఇది.

పండ్లోయమ్మ పండ్లు.. 

SONG COLLECTION: MANDHA RAMU

*అక్రమాసంబంధ0 పెట్టుకున్న.. ఓ ఇల్లాలును తన కొడుకు నిలదీయడంతో.. ప్రబుద్ధుడు చంపేస్తాడు. శవాన్ని పూడ్చే క్రమంలో ఎన్నెన్నో ఇబ్బందులు ఎదురౌతాయి. 
*దాంతో.. ఇంట్లో.. కొడుకుని నిలువునా కోసి.. ఉప్పుకారం దట్టించి.. కూర వండుతుంది. అనుకోకుండా అప్పుడే.. భర్త రావడంతో... అదే కూరను.. భర్తకు వడ్డిస్తుంది. 
*భర్త తింటావుంటే.. కంచంలో కొడుకు యొక్క వెండి ఉంగరం..  బంగారి గొలుసు కనబడుతుంది.
*అంతే... మళ్ళీ ఆ ప్రబుద్ధుడు వచ్చి భర్తని కొట్టి సంపుతాడు. 
*కానీ అదంతా గమనిస్తున్న దొంగలు.. ఇంటికి గడియవేసి.. నిప్పు పెడతారు.  దాంతో ఈ రంకు జంట కూడా బూడిద అయిపోతుంది. 

నీతి:  తాత్కాలిక ఆనందాల కోసం.. పాకులాడితే.. నా అనుకునే వాళ్లనే కాదు.. చివరికి తనకు తాను సర్వం కోల్పోతారు అని.. చాటి చెప్పే పాట ఇది.

పండ్లోయమ్మ పండ్లు..
